{
  "name": "steady",
  "duration_sec": 300,
  "arrival_rate_rps": 2,
  "concurrency_limit": 16,
  "timeout_sec": 60,
  "dataset": {
    "path": "evals/dataset.sample.jsonl"
  },
  "auth": {
    "auto_register": true,
    "password": "Password123"
  },
  "scenarios": [
    {
      "name": "single_turn_rag",
      "kind": "chat",
      "weight": 60,
      "query_source": "dataset",
      "turns": {
        "min": 1,
        "max": 1
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "multi_turn_rag",
      "kind": "chat",
      "weight": 15,
      "query_source": "dataset",
      "turns": {
        "min": 2,
        "max": 5
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "long_query",
      "kind": "chat",
      "weight": 10,
      "query_source": "inline",
      "queries": [
        "请基于知识库内容，系统性总结当前平台支持的工作流、适用场景、限制条件和推荐使用方式，并按重要程度排序。"
      ],
      "turns": {
        "min": 1,
        "max": 1
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "empty_retrieval",
      "kind": "chat",
      "weight": 5,
      "query_source": "inline",
      "queries": [
        "请解释一个知识库中不应存在的内部代号 zxqv-000-empty-retrieval 的上线策略。"
      ],
      "turns": {
        "min": 1,
        "max": 1
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "health_check",
      "kind": "health",
      "weight": 10
    }
  ]
}
